{"word":"G1630 - ἔκφοβος - ékphobos - ek'-fob-os - Sore afraid","sections":[{"paragraph":"<strong>மூல வார்த்தை / Original: </strong><span class=\"hebrewOrGreek\">ἔκφοβος</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>எழுத்துமாற்றம் / Transliteration: </strong><span class=\"transliteration\">ékphobos</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>ஒலிபெயர்ப்பு / Phonetic: </strong><span class=\"phonetic\">ek'-fob-os</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>சுருக்க விளக்கம் / Short Definition: </strong><span class=\"short-definition\">Sore afraid</span>"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"parts-of-speech\"><strong>இலக்கண சொல்வகை / Part(s) of speech: </strong>Adjective / பெயரடை</span>"},{"paragraph":"பயந்திருந்த, பயந்து நடுங்குகிற - பெயரடை"},{"paragraph":"stricken with fear or terror, exceedingly frightened, terrified"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"original-in-english\"><strong>ஆங்கில மூலம் / Original in English: </strong>From <a href=\"#/G1537 - ἐκ - ek - ek/1537\">G1537</a> and <a href=\"#/G5401 - φόβος - phóbos - fob'-os/5401\">G5401</a>; <i>frightened out</i> of one&rsquo;s wits: - sore afraid, exceedingly fear.</span>"},{"paragraph":""}]}